data.description: Stunning 4 bed 3 bath home with 2,262 square feet features an open concept layout highlighting all the modern finishes throughout. You will be impressed with the spacious great room w/ gas fireplace, new laminate flooring and ample natural light. The gourmet kitchen includes stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, custom shaker cabinets, and large breakfast bar with formal dining space. Relaxing main floor primary suite with luxe bathroom featuring a double vanity, large soaking tub, and floor to ceiling tile shower. Private junior suite upstairs with en-suite bath...perfect for guests. Spacious 3 car garage, fully fenced in private backyard with relaxing hot tub!
